body:
## Welcome to my personal site hosted on Github!

This will be my portfolio page, which will contain my work in web dev! I'm a beginner developer, and so I won't have some fancy site with all the cool animations and effects! I do however, have 4 below that I did as class projects(not too fancy, but the work of a newbie) :) !!

1. [DOM Manipulation](http://www.thomaskdesign.net/wats1020-dom-manipulation/)
2. [DOM Basics](http://www.thomaskdesign.net/wats1020-dom-basics/)
3. [Validating Form Data](http://www.thomaskdesign.net/wats1020-validating-form-data/)
4. [Imaginary Online Store-Html and CSS ](http://www.thomaskdesign.net/wats1010-product-page/)

And so, stay tuned! It will go through changes from time to time!

Come visit again in the not-so-distant future, and maybe I'll have something much better to showcase by then!!

© Thomas Kaiaua, 2016. Look me up on [Pinterest](https://www.pinterest.com/ThomasKaiaua/) and [Twitter](https://twitter.com/ThomasKaiaua).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
